    <section id="features">
      <h2>📌 Unique Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>📖 <strong>Church Planting 1–4</strong> is mandatory before graduation</li>
        <li>🛠️ Electives designed to help pastors earn while ministering</li>
        <li>🌆 Special focus on urban ministry settings</li>
        <li>✝️ CAMACOP Statement of Faith</li>
        <li>🧾 <strong>No thesis required</strong> — Instead, students submit a <strong>1-year ministry reflection</strong> and a <strong>practical church planting proposal</strong> based on real experience</li>
      </ul>
